{"id": 1075, "genre": 1000, "title": "对于会员卡这个东西，你有什么要吐槽的？", "description": "身无分文，也不妨碍我成为一代卡王。（题图来自：Thomas Hedger）", "record_count": 8113, "comment_count": 27, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130142FQ9REUBJ7bkvXNZY.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-27T01:00:06Z", "questions": [{"id": 956, "title": "对于会员卡这个东西，你有什么要吐槽的？", "content": "对于会员卡这个东西，你有什么要吐槽的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 92230, "content": "努力攒了几个月的积分，到年底清零了", "image": "img/option/option/20160703183153UwjbfImKpd57g2zT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 92231, "content": "为了凑积分或满减，莫名其妙增加了消费", "image": "img/option/option/20160703183154meQMPi9w0tfBnINK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 92236, "content": "好些时候想要享受优惠，还要先存钱进去", "image": "img/option/option/201607031831549ZEMTkRQByJYOcVb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 92237, "content": "促销规则傻傻分不清楚", "image": "img/option/option/20160703130015TocyXhsP216v9jzd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 92238, "content": "要登记各种个人信息", "image": "img/option/option/201607031300056XO4MItRyxadmkWZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 92239, "content": "明明只是偶尔消费一次，却被店员一直追着问要不要办卡", "image": "img/option/option/20160703183154Hr0FkvzlqfyTBRUW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 92241, "content": "有些店要求带实体卡，谁愿意多带一张卡出门？", "image": "img/option/option/20160703181318EjX1xiH7kAeSuvJT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 92242, "content": "微信/支付宝扫码付了个钱之后，就自动成了会员", "image": "img/option/option/201607031300186bjz8Fikw3ENQvCG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 92244, "content": "手机上每天收到商家的促销信息", "image": "img/option/option/20160703183155ZQ7DIO1WdyCHhU9T.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}